original_title: Medvedev says European leaders 'failed to outplay' Trump on Ukraine | Fox News
article_summary: Former Russian President Dmitry Medvedev criticizes European leaders for allegedly failing to outplay U.S. President Donald Trump during a meeting with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy. Medvedev mocks Zelenskyy and questions his stance on security guarantees for Ukraine, following Trump's meeting with Zelenskyy and a trilateral meeting with Russian President Vladimir Putin being proposed.</s>
